38:01.908 --> 38:03.827
FEMALE VOICE: You have three new messages.

38:03.828 --> 38:05.947
Gus [over phone]: Joel, call
me when you get this.

38:05.948 --> 38:08.107
We are booked on a 5:00 P.M. flight.

38:08.108 --> 38:09.307
Just get to the airport.

38:09.308 --> 38:10.947
Everything's waiting for you at the desk.

38:10.948 --> 38:12.667
Ticket, passport.

38:12.668 --> 38:14.147
I'll explain when you get here.

38:14.148 --> 38:15.588
We are going home.

38:21.468 --> 38:23.348
[phone chirps]

38:41.308 --> 38:42.947
Oh, it...

38:42.948 --> 38:45.187
broke.

38:45.188 --> 38:47.827
We've printed your travel details,

38:47.828 --> 38:49.947
and the wire is still going through.

38:49.948 --> 38:51.427
Just a minute.

38:51.428 --> 38:53.347
Have you enjoyed Belize?

38:53.348 --> 38:54.947
Sure.

38:54.948 --> 38:57.707
Uh, well, a bit mixed.

38:57.708 --> 38:59.429
If I'm being honest.

39:00.108 --> 39:01.387
But it ended well.

39:01.388 --> 39:03.166
Mm, so you have friends here?

39:03.292 --> 39:04.307
No.

39:04.308 --> 39:05.206
Yes.

39:05.207 --> 39:07.366
I mean, I... I came here with friends.

39:09.108 --> 39:11.027
It's hard, traveling with friends.

39:11.028 --> 39:14.107
You think you know people, but
when you travel together,

39:14.108 --> 39:16.148
that's when you really get to know them.

39:17.642 --> 39:19.682
Yeah, that's so true.

39:22.308 --> 39:24.027
♪

39:24.028 --> 39:26.227
But in the end, you
know, you just got to...

39:27.428 --> 39:29.232
take care of yourself, right?

39:35.788 --> 39:37.227
