as soon as we can.

39:48.628 --> 39:49.787
How you feeling? You okay?

39:49.788 --> 39:51.458
I mean, apart from the...

39:52.570 --> 39:54.182
Gus: You're getting a promotion, right?

39:54.183 --> 39:55.387
Rochelle: What makes you say that?

39:55.388 --> 39:56.427
The card on your desk said,

39:56.428 --> 39:57.667
"Congratulations on a promotion."

39:57.668 --> 39:59.450
Or the-the lady in the hallway that said,

39:59.451 --> 40:00.772
"Congratulations on a promotion."

40:02.395 --> 40:05.346
Lex: What you did took some balls,
I'll say that.

40:05.661 --> 40:06.755
Excuse me?

40:07.908 --> 40:08.908
Not giving up.

40:09.388 --> 40:10.667
[Rochelle scoffs]

40:10.668 --> 40:11.885
Gus [whispering]: Which way is it?

40:11.886 --> 40:12.705
You know what?

40:12.730 --> 40:14.463
Why do people use that expression?

40:14.464 --> 40:16.387
Have you ever seen a man
be kicked in the balls?

40:16.388 --> 40:17.970
- Oh, yeah.
- Yeah, so have I.

40:17.971 --> 40:19.267
He's rendered completely immobile,

40:19.268 --> 40:21.092
