40:21.093 --> 40:23.099
When did balls become
the symbol of strength?

40:23.100 --> 40:23.662
Wow.

40:23.663 --> 40:25.077
Why not a vagina, you know?

40:25.628 --> 40:27.747
I mean, vaginas take a pounding
most of their adult life.

40:27.748 --> 40:28.896
What you should have said was,

40:28.897 --> 40:32.011
"What you did, that took some vagina,
I'll say that."

40:32.012 --> 40:33.949
Can we just make a stop before
we get to the airport?

40:33.950 --> 40:35.489
Are you serious? You fu...

40:37.348 --> 40:39.068
♪

40:51.908 --> 40:53.187
Please don't freak out.

40:53.188 --> 40:55.947
[scoffs] Who's freaking out?

40:55.948 --> 40:57.827
I don't want your apologies.

40:57.828 --> 40:58.837
Who's apologizing?

40:59.478 --> 41:00.867
Frankly, I don't have

41:00.868 --> 41:02.307
another apology left in me.

41:02.308 --> 41:03.468
[scoffs] So what do you want?

41:03.858 --> 41:07.147
Um, I'm traveling tonight

41:07.148 --> 41:10.507
and, uh, wanted to get a
tin of those hard candies.

41:10.508 --> 41:11.589
You guys sell those, right?

41:11.988 --> 41:13.192
You came to make jokes?

41:13.193 --> 41:15.227
No. Look...

41:15.228 --> 41:17.227
Look, I-I know your family's pretty upset

41:17.228 --> 41:19.027
- about what happened to the dog.
- Only Aunt Shiraine.

41:19.028 --> 41:21.107
The rest of us were really
not that fond of...

41:21.108 --> 41:23.326
- Not that we would have wished.
- No, of course.

41:24.188 --> 41:27.108
I've seen some terrible things
since I've been here.

41:29.428 --> 41:31.147
I've seen some beautiful
and amazing things, too.

41:31.148 --> 41:34.718
C-Certainly things that
I'm never gonna forget,

41:34.719 --> 41:37.827
but I got to get back to Chicago.

41:37.828 --> 41:38.858
Erica: To your children?

41:38.883 --> 41:39.883
Yeah.

41:40.388 --> 41:42.507
To whom I will always be an embarrassment

41:42.508 --> 41:43.795
and a disappointment.

41:43.796 --> 41:45.636
Despite what I'd like to believe,
that is the truth.

41:45.637 --> 41:46.793
Well, you're their father.

41:46.818 --> 41:47.934
It's your job.

41:48.474 --> 41:49.848
Can you explain to me

41:49.873 --> 41:52.027
how a shitty guy gets such a beautiful job?

41:52.028 --> 41:53.507
[chuckles] You may be a bullshitter,

41:53.508 --> 41:54.674
but you're not a shitty guy.

41:55.144 --> 41:56.588
That's why I came to help you.

41:57.947 --> 41:59.267
Yeah.

41:59.268 --> 42:01.547
So if a bullshitter sent you a ticket,

42:02.322 --> 42:04.508
you think you'd want to come visit Chicago?

42:06.335 --> 42:07.714
You send the ticket,

42:08.428 --> 42:10.028
and I'll let you know.

42:14.548 --> 42:16.028
Thank you.

42:28.028 --> 42:29.683
Lex: Maybe they lost their phones,

42:29.684 --> 42:30.925
or they're not charged...

42:30.926 --> 42:32.987
Gus: Then they won't get my messages.

42:32.988 --> 42:34.787
- We should stay.
- With you in this condition?

42:34.788 --> 42:37.628
Man, we got to get you home, ASAP.

42:39.148 --> 42:40.587
Cobi!

42:40.588 --> 42:43.547
Dude... man.

42:43.548 --> 42:45.027
You got my message!

42:45.028 --> 42:46.336
- Yeah. Yeah.
- Damn.

42:47.797 --> 42:49.100
Cobi: Hey, Lex.

42:49.101 --> 42:50.686
How you doing? You okay?

42:50.687 --> 42:53.427
- Yeah.
- Well, that's a relief, huh?

42:53.428 --> 42:54.563
Where's Joel?

42:54.564 --> 42:56.939
I... I assumed he was gonna be
with you guys.

42:56.964 --> 42:57.827
Gus: Well, we just gotta give him

42:57.828 --> 42:58.907
a little bit of time. He'll be here.

42:58.908 --> 43:00.107
Hey, where... where'd you go

43:00.108 --> 43:01.188
when you left the hospital?

43:01.631 --> 43:03.387
I, uh... just went out.

43:03.388 --> 43:04.474
Get some air.

43:04.475 --> 43:06.169
- For ten hours, you went to get some air?

43:06.170 --> 43:07.256
Gus: First-class ticket.

43:07.507 --> 43:09.427
Yeah, I... used my miles

43:09.428 --> 43:10.245
to get an upgrade.

43:10.246 --> 43:11.832
- You got my message?
- Yeah.

43:11.910 --> 43:12.987
- My message?
- Yeah.

43:12.988 --> 43:13.979
Well, what-what did it say?

43:13.980 --> 43:14.807
"Meet us at the airport."

43:14.808 --> 43:15.823
Gus: What else?

43:17.388 --> 43:18.388
"See you there."

43:18.389 --> 43:21.027
Who got these for us, Cobi?

43:21.028 --> 43:22.627
I... I don't...

43:22.628 --> 43:24.187
What's going on, Cobi?

43:24.188 --> 43:25.370
- What's going on?
- No, no, no.

43:25.371 --> 43:27.385
Just because we, you know,
traveled here together

43:27.386 --> 43:28.847
